- Assumed/unverified: the exact npm package name `agentos`, the import path `agentos/software/pi`, and the Pi session method name — I built `lib/pi-adapter.mjs` specifically so this is a one-line fix if the real surface differs (e.g., `session.run()` instead of `session.act()`).

